1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,800
Science has a clearer story about heat pumps than social media does.

2
00:00:04,800 --> 00:00:08,000
Heat pumps don’t create heat; they move it.

3
00:00:08,000 --> 00:00:10,800
Think of them as refrigerators in reverse.

4
00:00:10,800 --> 00:00:12,800
But, is this technology efficient?

5
00:00:12,800 --> 00:00:14,800
It depends on your climate.

6
00:00:14,800 --> 00:00:20,400
Studies show they can reduce energy costs by up to 50% in moderate climates.

7
00:00:20,400 --> 00:00:23,200
However, in extreme weather, they may struggle.

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:24,800
So, know your environment.

9
00:00:24,800 --> 00:00:26,800
Curious about other eco-friendly tech?

10
00:00:26,800 --> 00:00:29,200
